The paper deals with clustering of spatial datasets, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and data science (cs.DS). The approach presented in the paper involves local clustering and aggregation, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also focuses on efficiency and accuracy, which are topics of interest in statistical learning (cs.LG) and computational intelligence (cs.SI).
